data.description: Single story and large floorplan located in the wonderful Heritage Lakes Community! Tiled entry and nice open formal living room area with cutouts to the hallway allow for an open flow floorplan. The Family room offers a fireplace and adjacent the kitchen for a great room vibe. Kitchen has lots of cabinets and granite counters with stainless appliances. There are bedrooms all on one side of the house with an office area near the kitchen. Master bedroom is large and faces the rear of the home. Back patio has aluma wood cover and shed. There is a 3 car tandem garage, great for additional storage. Offerings include 2 Jr. Olympic size pools, a Splash Park, a wading pool, 3 tot-lot playgrounds, paddleboats to explore the 25-acre lake, catch-and-release fishing, clubhouse facility, fitness trail lake path with exercise equipment. Heritage Lakes is located close to the 215/15 freeways.
